{"tid":913322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大粉塵爆炸：仔兩成皮膚燒傷母心痛玩大咗","createTime":"2018-11-23T10:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T10:26:04.000Z","uid":211565,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7f25a7cb0f833b50b09ad5c55cffde41323b19ab","tid":913322,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:18:14.000Z","msg":"浸會大學南座偉倫樓學生宿舍昨日(22日)發生麵粉塵爆意外，有份出席慶生的一名21歲姓周壽星仔，因身體約有兩成皮膚燒傷，今日(23日)仍在沙田威爾斯醫院留醫。其母親及胞弟今午前往探望。據周母心痛表示，今次「真係玩大咗，玩得過分，有啲嬲」，只好當汲取一個教訓。 <br />\n<br />\n周的胞弟坦言，最初獲悉意外時，不知道兄長受傷，故第一時間也<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">感到出事的學生「好幼稚」</span></span>，但獲悉兄長涉及意外受傷後，便覺得自己<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「好涼薄」</span></span>，故希望社會大眾也能有同理心，不要過度問責追究學生。另外，浸大亦派出一男一女職員到醫院探望。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，周在浸大就讀人力資源學系二年級，雖然已過了生日，但昨凌晨出席宿舍的「每月之星」補祝生日時，遇上塵爆意外燒傷。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=AQftnGCaSe8XZIqBl4ISuYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ed33a70d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a> 東網報導"},{"pid":"4424513ff49090173f2bc17982f0284e13d25535","tid":913322,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58700e6d0063eaa2fe49c10e5718b361184b9cf2","tid":913322,"uid":211565,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"你老母都嫌你幼稚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434fe1ec171795331b85a18528f079f05d6fc74c","tid":913322,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 涼薄"},{"pid":"f038f4d9dbbd0518a8e64a7e47652fdc288a0619","tid":913322,"uid":31522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1409d7e4e4542d4754c67c77eb5c9b64877cf136","tid":913322,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"柒足一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁過關家姐"},{"pid":"06fcbd7a14d4c24c82f7d95972074283e842a8fd","tid":913322,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"哎喲 無陰公囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dea32b5683d6534971caf489868876baa74dad1","tid":913322,"uid":79144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"雖然通常壽星仔都係比人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}